  "permissions": "Requires authentication. Admins can update any question. Non-admins can update questions they asked, but cannot change asked_by; changing public organization scope requires membership in both the previous and new scope; toggling is_public or is_public_to_organization_children is only allowed for the asking user. Non-admins cannot update motivation, is_triaged, or assigned_to.",
