  "validation_notes": "Boolean flags require true/false values (ignore_organization_scoped_newsletters, is_public, is_public_to_organization_children, is_triaged, recreate_answer). At least one attribute or relationship must be changed; otherwise the request is rejected. --asked-by cannot be empty when provided. --public-organization-scope cannot be combined with --public-organization-scope-type or --public-organization-scope-id. --public-organization-scope must be formatted as type|id; --public-organization-scope-type and --public-organization-scope-id must be provided together. public_organization_scope must be a valid organization type (Broker, Customer, Trucker, MaterialSupplier, or Developer). assigned_to must be an admin user."
